====== Curriculum 2013 ======

===== Book =====
 
//Computers as Components: Principles of Embedded Computer System Design by Marilyn Wolf//. The whole book is part of the curriculum. Both second and third editions can be used. 

===== Exercises =====

The exercise documentation and knowledge required to do the exercises is on the curriculum. This includes understanding C and assembly code.

===== Lectures =====

The provided lecture slides are part of the curriculum. This includes slides from guest lectures. 

===== Recommended Reading =====

We recommend buying a book on the C programming language. Our recommendation is //Brian W. Kernighan and Dennis M. Ritchie. The C Programming Language. Prentice Hall Software Series, 2nd edition, 1988//.